data.description: Welcome to your coastal oasis in Seclusion Beach, part of the exclusive Bid A Wee Beach community with private beach access!  This fully renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom single-family home offers the epitome of coastal elegance.  Enjoy the serenity of a fully fenced yard, relax in the outdoor hot tub or beneath the hot water outdoor shower, and soak in the coastal vibe on your spacious 12x50 covered back porch.This residence features granite countertops, tiled walk-in showers, 10 ft ceilings, and crown molding in select areas, adding a touch of elegance.With an oversized single car garage and an extended driveway for multiple vehicles, parking is a breeze. Located in a highly desirable school district, this home provides the perfect combination of convenience and beach living. Don't miss the chance to call this slice of paradise your own - schedule your showing today!
